	(text "SYSTEM INTERFACE & RATING SPECIFICATIONS:\n\n[BATT_MAIN]: XT30 Input (VBAT_RAW_IN)\n- Continuous Current Rating: 15A (30A Peak). \n- Routing: Traces to DJI output must be routed as power polygons on both Top and Bottom layers. Remove soldermask for heavy tin plating.\n\n[BATT_CELLS]: JST-XH-4P Balance Input\n- Max rating per cell pin: 4.35V (LiHV standard).\n- Total series max voltage: 13.05V.\n\n[ICSP_HEADER]: AVR Programming (2x3 Pin 2.54mm)\n- TARGET VOLTAGE (VTG): 3.3V. \n- DO NOT USE 5V PROGRAMMERS WITHOUT LOGIC LEVEL SHIFTERS. Direct 5V exposure on ICSP lines will irreversibly damage the 3.3V onboard LDO/Buck and INA199 current sense amplifier."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 149.86 130.81 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "b6cb1c0b-e6e3-45b8-95b6-43e6f1bf41b4")
	)
